  "title": "History & Culture - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1892109_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1892109_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">History &amp; Culture</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\" width=\"100%\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6279786\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>Although the Grand Canyon is known around the world for its vast vistas, beautiful colors, and incredible geology, it's a lot more than just a big hole in the ground!  People have been living in and exploring Grand Canyon for thousands of years, forging human connections to this incredible landscape.<br/>\n<br/>\nAs part of the mission of the National Park Service, Grand Canyon National Park also protects and preserves all of the human history and culture found within the park. From archeological sites which preserve ancient Native American structures and artifacts, to stories about exploration and the settlement of this region by European American explorers, miners, and pioneers, to more recent stories about conserving and protecting Grand Canyon as a national park.<br/>\n<br/>\nThis incredible place tells innumerable stories left by the many different people who have tread here in the past.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6280272\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6280272\">\n<div class=\"Component FeatureGrid\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -large\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/interp_themes.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/interp_themes.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"The grand canyon at sunset.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 1300px, (min-width: 1200px) 1120px, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8765050-D5D5-F17A-E4416D2141527801.jpg?width=1300&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8765050-D5D5-F17A-E4416D2141527801.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8765050-D5D5-F17A-E4416D2141527801.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8765050-D5D5-F17A-E4416D2141527801.jpg?width=1300&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 1300w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Interpretive Themes</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Interpretive themes are the key stories or concepts that visitors should understand after visiting Grand Canyon.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/people.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/people.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A cemetery gate.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/2ABB3BB4-C520-BCEC-5692496683F5C07C.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/2ABB3BB4-C520-BCEC-5692496683F5C07C.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/2ABB3BB4-C520-BCEC-5692496683F5C07C.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">People</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Passing through or calling the canyon home, many people have influenced the development and protection of Grand Canyon.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/places.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/places.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Two people sitting at a picnic table with a stone building in the background.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B7E60F31-A25E-DCAB-AA16ACC461D78575.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B7E60F31-A25E-DCAB-AA16ACC461D78575.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B7E60F31-A25E-DCAB-AA16ACC461D78575.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Places</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Many places in Grand Canyon have been preserved because they tell the stories of Grand Canyon's past and present.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/collections.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/collections.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A Havasupai woven basket.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8F605A0-AA63-6504-4BE0955BBABB8ED1.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8F605A0-AA63-6504-4BE0955BBABB8ED1.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B8F605A0-AA63-6504-4BE0955BBABB8ED1.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Collections</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Museum Collection has over 900,000 objects that help tell Grand Canyon's unique cultural and natural history.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/preservation.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/preservation.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Walhalla Ruin\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B9A144A8-ABB4-0D9F-4355F2D3C29FF6F8.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B9A144A8-ABB4-0D9F-4355F2D3C29FF6F8.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/B9A144A8-ABB4-0D9F-4355F2D3C29FF6F8.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Preservation</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Grand Canyon National Park works to preserve, protect and interpret the human history of the region.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/whose-story-is-history.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/whose-story-is-history.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Images of Nampeyo, CCC members, Pauline Patraw Mead, and George Murakami. \" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/BEF9A18D-9C44-5849-277F2D3E3CAA7351.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/BEF9A18D-9C44-5849-277F2D3E3CAA7351.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/BEF9A18D-9C44-5849-277F2D3E3CAA7351.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Whose Story Is History?</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Bringing the Diverse History of Grand Canyon into the Light</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/getinvolved/centennial.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/getinvolved/centennial.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Painting of Grand Canyon with text that reads 1919-2019 Grand Canyon National Park Centennial\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/BF04A190-A707-019E-30590241AA2C2323.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/BF04A190-A707-019E-30590241AA2C2323.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/BF04A190-A707-019E-30590241AA2C2323.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Grand Canyon Centennial Stories</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Explore the Grand Canyon Centennial Stories</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2320127\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2320127\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<a href=\"http://grcahistory.org/\">\n<img alt=\"Banner image linking to ASU Nature, Culture and History at the Grand Canyon shows Grand Canyon scenic view with superimposed letters: ASU Nature, Culture and History at the Grand Canyon\" src=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/images/asu-banner960-jpg.JPG?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<figcaption>The \"Nature, Culture and History at Grand Canyon\" website is the park's primary source of historical and cultural information, Click on the photo above to visit site. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x2x1\" width=\"100%\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"/commonspot/images/clear.gif\" style=\"display:block;\" width=\"1\"/></td></tr><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x3x1\" width=\"100%\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"/commonspot/images/clear.gif\" style=\"display:block;\" width=\"1\"/></td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: February 14, 2022</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
